    "James W. Knox": "goes on to say, And hath raised us up together, and made us sit together in heavenly places in Christ Jesus `[char_Jesus_Ref]`. I got out of Adam `[char_Adam_Luk_3]` and into Jesus `[char_Jesus_Ref]` Christ. How did that happen? God did it by His grace. \u201cWell how ? I do not understand. \u201d No one does, but let us see what the Bible says. Paul `[char_Paul_Act_13]`, a servant of God, and an apostle of Jesus `[char_Jesus_Ref]` Christ, according to THE FAITH OF GOD \u2019S ELECT\u2026 (Titus 1:1). Who is God \u2019s elect ? That is Jesus `[char_Jesus_Ref]` Christ. How do you know that when you call on Him you will have eternal life and not just life as long as you can hold onto it? Because your life is secured by the faith of Jesus `[char_Jesus_Ref]` Christ. Do you want a cross-reference to put in your margin? Go to Galatians 2:\nVerse 6 goes on to say, And hath raised us up together, and made us sit together in heavenly places in Christ Jesus `[char_Jesus_Ref]`. I got out of Adam `[char_Adam_Luk_3]` and into Jesus `[char_Jesus_Ref]` Christ. How did that happen? God did it by His grace. \u201cWell how? I do not understand.\u201d No one does, but let us see what the Bible says. Paul `[char_Paul_Act_13]`, a servant of God, and an apostle of Jesus `[char_Jesus_Ref]` Christ, [v_Tit_1_1] according to THE FAITH OF GOD\u2019S ELECT\u2026 (Titus `[char_Titus_Gal_2]` 1:1). Who is God\u2019s elect? That is Jesus `[char_Jesus_Ref]` Christ. How do you know that when you call on Him you will have eternal life and not just life as long as you can hold onto it? Because your life is secured by the faith of Jesus `[char_Jesus_Ref]` Christ. Do you want a cross-reference to put in your margin? [v_Gal_2_20] Go to Galatians 2:",
